Approaches
1) entering wifi...ping mobile IP address -  wifi return IP address

2) geofencing mobile app will send notification email/sms when enters 100m geofence area
RPI will read email ...decode word

3) GPS hardware GTO will SEND  1 & 0 to RPI  whenever geofence border is entered  




